reviews.text: A very special and famous duck soup hot pot. You will leave the shop with the smell all around your clothes :P
Nice and reasonable price

Noisy Hong Kong hotpot. The food quality is good. If you don't know Cantonese. It will be a difficult place to dine in. But if you're a local, you'll find enjoyment there with your friends or family having a traditional hotpot.
Been to that place with my mates for years. Excellent place for gathering with my old mates!

24.8.2017: highly recommended 
soup base is excellent, food is above average, servers are well trained, awesome..
